name: Volt Inu [OLD]
public_notice: Volt Inu has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. Visit this post for more information and visit the new token page here.

description.en: Volt Inu ($VOLT) is a hyper-deflationary token whose aim is to invest in multiple asset classes such as NFTs, nodes, altcoins, staking & farming of stablecoins. Unlike FaaS projects, this investement diversity allows to mitigate the risk while taking advantage of the possible non-correlated growth of the trending assets.
